ers and development can be picked up by othersgversionl1.17.0-beta1ldownload_urlxshttps://github.com/cryptomator/cryptomator/releases/download/1.17.0-beta1/cryptomator-1.17.0-beta1-aarch64.AppImagedsizeh53.03 MBhsrc_urlsüx3https://github.com/cryptomator/cryptomator/releaseshweb_urlsüxhttps://github.com/cryptomatorglicenseüpGPL-3.0-or-laterkmaintainersx9AppImage (https://github.com/AppImage/appimage.github.io)enotesçx:[EXTERNAL] (This is an unofficial, third-party repository)xI[UNTRUSTED] (We CAN NOT guarantee the authenticity, validity or security)x2This data was autogenerated & is likely inaccuratex/Data used: https://appimage.github.io/feed.jsonx;Provided by: https://github.com/AppImage/appimage.github.ioxNLearn More: https://docs.pkgforge.dev/repositories/external/appimage.github.iox;Please create an Issue or send a PR for an official PackageČcpkgodbgate.appimagehpkg_namefdbgatefpkg_idx appimage.github.io.DbGate.dbgatekdescriptionx'Opensource database administration toolgversionfv6.5.4ldownload_urlxVhttps://github.com/dbgate/dbgate/releases/download/v6.5.4/dbgate-latest-arm64.AppImagedsizei151.97 MBhsrc_urlsüx)https://github.com/dbgate/dbgate/releaseshweb_urlsüxhttps://github.com/dbgateglicenseücMITkmaintainersx9AppImage (https://github.com/AppImage/appimage.github.io)enotesçx:[EXTERNAL] (This is an unofficial, third-party repository)xI[UNTRUSTED] (We CAN NOT guarantee the authenticity, validity or security)x2This data was autogenerated & is likely inaccuratex/Data used: https://appimage.github.io/feed.jsonx;Provided by: https://github.com/AppImage/appimage.github.ioxNLearn More: https://docs.pkgforge.dev/repositories/external/appimage.github.iox;Please create an Issue or send a PR for an official PackageČcpkgqeasyedit.appimagehpkg_nameheasyeditfpkg_idx$appimage.github.io.EasyEdit.gcclinuxkdescriptionx1A lightweight Markdown editor built with Electrongversione1.3.7ldownload_urlxZhttps://github.com/gcclinux/EasyEdit/releases/download/1.3.7/EasyEdit-1.3.7-arm64.A